   "source": [
    "#### GD"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "064dbf53",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\theta_t = \\theta_{t-1} - \\eta_t g_{t-1}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7bb23901",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Momentum"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "79d771a3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$m_t = \\beta m_{t-1} + g_{t-1}$$\n",
    "$$\\theta_t = \\theta_{t-1} - \\eta_t m_t$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0ef70fcf",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Nesterov step"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a4e9631d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$m_{t+1} = \\beta m_t - \\eta_t \\nabla L(\\theta_t + \\beta m_t)$$\n",
    "$$\\theta_{t+1} = \\theta_t + m_{t+1}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9751bc3e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": []
  }
